\b Actions
\b0 \
\
- Collapse / Expand - The Notes section can be collapsed, or expanded\
\
- Add - The user can add a Note by clicking on the add butcon displayed in the panel header\
  -- After clicking on the add action, a dialog will display in which the user can type their note and save it\
  -- New notes will display at the top of the Notes list\
\
